Hi, FEUture nurses! 👋 Selling my sister’s nursing textbooks:

• Brunner & Suddarth's Med-Surg Nursing, 15th Ed.
(Vols. 1-2 + Study Guide) - P3,000 (Vols. 1-2:
Unused, Study Guide: 3 pages may sulat can provide photo for reference)

• NANDA, 15th Ed. - P500 (Minimal underlinings on one page, like may na underline lang na one word hahaha)

Name written below and above the sides of book and in the back of front page (sides can be cut and removed at Recto for a minimal fee)

📍Manila City: Meetups in:
- FEU (not inside the campus) 
- España
- Balic-Balic area.

💰MOP: Gcash/Bank/Cash
Reason for Selling: Decluttering / Alumni na

Note: DM me if interested!
